premise_source_doc_sentence: Russi is a comune  (  municipality  )  in the Province of Ravenna in the Italian region Emilia-Romagna , located about 60 km east of Bologna and about 14 km southwest of Ravenna .
Beyond Jazz was the name of XM Satellite Radio 's Commercial-Free Modern Jazz music channel , devoted to Modern Jazz , Funk-jazz , Free jazz and Acid jazz music .
The channel was described as `` The greats of the Jazz-fusion era , stars of Modern Electric and Acoustic Jazz , The New Jazz Singers , The Jazzy Jambands , Acid jazz and Techno Jazz . ''
The program director for Beyond Jazz was Russ Davis .

The program director , Russ Davis , along with the host of `` Jammin ' Jazz '' , Michelle Sammartino have launched a website which promises to provide programming similar to that which aired on the now defunct channel .
Beyond Jazz was removed from XM 's lineup on November 12 , 2008 .
